der to prevent this trend from continuing, warehouse workers must unite themselves, speak up and fight for the formation of a union.\n\nMarco shares his story with other workers still employed at various warehouses in the region to help inform them of what he has learned. He hopes that by doing this they will be able to protect themselves and avoid being placed in dangerous situations.', 'Former Warehouse Worker Interviews', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '805-revision-2', '', '', '2012-04-22 08:06:34', '2012-04-22 08:06:34', '', 805, 'http://empirelogistics.org/uncategorized/805-revision-2/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
