nity Action and Environmental Justice (CCAEJ) is attempting to pressure local government to better regulate air quality in Mia Loma, which has some of the worst air pollution in the country.\n\nWe seek to facilitate direct response to immediate social problems through accessible technology; the stimulation of a collective and participatory action that bypasses official media channels; and the forging of community and solidarity between related struggles.', 'ABOUT', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '696-revision-v1', '', '', '2010-09-19 21:27:56', '2010-09-20 02:27:56', '', 696, 'http://empirelogistics.org/uncategorized/696-revision/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
