(2504, 1, '2013-06-13 04:17:14', '2013-06-13 04:17:14', '<address>(Cut and Paste the text below into a new post)</address>\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n<h3>Brief Overview</h3>\r\n<h3>List of Core Administrators</h3>\r\n<h3><strong>General information:</strong></h3>\r\n<h4><em>City and State in which port is located:</em></h4>\r\n<h4><em>Name of Port Authority/Commission: </em></h4>\r\n<h4><em>Port’s website:</em></h4>\r\n<h4><em>Name and location of Major Container Terminal(s): </em></h4>\r\n<h4><em>Demographics of surrounding area: </em></h4>\r\nAverage household size ,\r\n\r\nAverage family size\r\n\r\nIn labor force (16yrs +)\r\n\r\nMedian household income\r\n\r\nFamilies below poverty level\r\n\r\nTotal population\r\n\r\nRace:\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3><strong>Economics of Port:</strong></h3>\r\n<h4><em>Rank in North American Container Volume by TEUs in 2009 (from AAPA):</em></h4>\r\n<h4><em>Container volume in TEUs 2012 (from AAPA):</em></h4>\r\n<h4><em>Imports and exports:</em></h4>\r\nImports Loaded-\r\nExports Loaded-\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3><strong>Port expansion:</strong></h3>\r\n<h4><em>Is port expanding? To what location? What is the cost of expansion?</em></h4>\r\n<h4><em>What interests and/or individuals are driving expansion plans?</em></h4>\r\n<h4><em>Any special funds involved in Port/interstate/railyard expansion? How much, and for what project?</em></h4>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3><strong>Connected facilities:</strong></h3>\r\n<h4><em>Is highway expansion predicted in connection with port expansion? What highway/interstate?</em></h4>\r\n<h4><em>Are there any intermodal facilities connected to this port? If so, what railroad and location of facility:</em></h4>\r\n<h4><em>Are there any warehouses or distribution center complexes that service this port? If so, where? Yes, but no warehouses, the following are distribution centers:</em></h4>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3><strong>Environmental Issues</strong></h3>\r\n<h4><em>Press about environmental issues:</em></h4>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3><strong>News stories</strong></h3>\r\n<h4><em>Are there any news stories about environmental problems (water/air/noise/traffic/lights)?</em></h4>\r\n<h4><em>EIR/EISs. Any environmental reviews (EISs/EAs) mentioned in the news media file?</em></h4>\r\n<h4><em>Are there any emissions inventories conducted on this port?</em></h4>\r\n<h4><em>Does the website indicate that the port does air monitoring? </em></h4>\r\n<h4><em>Are there any environmental concerns/interests/protests/lawsuits from the public about port expansion or operations?</em></h4>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h3><strong>Community Participation</strong></h3>\r\n<h4><em>Are port authority meetings open to the public?</em></h4>\r\n<h4><em>Is the public given a role and determining authority at commission meetings?</em></h4>\r\n<h4><em>Are Commission minutes posted online?</em></h4>\r\n<h4><em>Is there a community benefits agreement related to this Port?</em></h4>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n____________', 'Port of Richmond', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', '2297-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-06-13 04:17:14', '2013-06-13 04:17:14', '', 2297, 'http://empire-logistics.org/uncategorized/2297-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
